```r
tidy_telecomms <- telecomms_churn %>% 
  drop_na() %>% 
  select(-customer_id) %>% 
  mutate(senior_citizen = factor(senior_citizen,
                                    levels = c(0, 1),
                                    labels = c("true", "false"))
         ) %>% 
  mutate_if(is.character, as.factor)
  
```
